data.description: PRICE DROP!!! This updated rambler boasts an inviting open floor plan, creating a seamless flow throughout the main house. Inside, discover three spacious bedrooms and two full baths, offering comfort and style.  But the charm doesn't stop there – attached is a mother in law suite with its own kitchenette, bedroom, and full bath, providing versatility for guests or potential rental income.  Step outside into your private oasis – a backyard featuring a shed for storage, a delightful patio for entertaining, and a gazebo for those tranquil moments under the stars.  Convenience is key with this property, as it's in close proximity to the base, restaurants, shopping, and various amenities. Embrace the perfect blend of modern living and practicality in this thoughtfully designed home. Your oasis awaits!
